{"tid":1631450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際文宣：terrorism in Hong Kong","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:53:04.000Z","uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bb39931eef7eac430668c39c410a8fe08e4cf719","tid":1631450,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:33:05.000Z","msg":"搞大左淋病死十次都唔掂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea517fa51fc7c4a25a95a84a8ad36fbbf187d1f7","tid":1631450,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:33:22.000Z","msg":"對店舖:<br />\n記住<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔需要次次硬裝修</span></span></strong><br />\n可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">善用</span><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蟲系魔法</span></strong></span>同埋<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1823</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對人(影大頭相/非主攻類):<br />\n可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong><br />\n唔係下下爆哂缸先叫成功既<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要贏一定要剛柔並用</span>"},{"pid":"380398d4dd654b27107460047c2945383a8c6fc6","tid":1631450,"uid":75959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"43da039f6d8e30cf2b6f3bdc294e42a7a1aaf100","tid":1631450,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:36:39.000Z","msg":"淨係今日深水埗汽車故意撞落人群已經係恐怖襲擊級數"},{"pid":"37fb8843f4daf68d1b39f9fde644a8ed8f01e390","tid":1631450,"uid":322124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:37:02.000Z","msg":"[本土文宣+國際戰線] 撤銷緊急法 !!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1631430/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1631430/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"dff027566f187c098e2fc6375a47e13d3d2a16e7","tid":1631450,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:38:50.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"789df80594468d6ba164739db1229439bbba0f6d","tid":1631450,"uid":161848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:45:19.000Z","msg":"[屌你地快入嚟幫拖] 五毛藍屍已開始打國際戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631332\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631332</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6f0cc0c79b74f2bde801a10f0e8a51dc0a11233d","tid":1631450,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:46:03.000Z","msg":"推呢個啦，其他都垃圾"},{"pid":"2c0ab00f04f36946fc21e8ddbcd1eb322d5071df","tid":1631450,"uid":75543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:46:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>做文宣 永不割蓆</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4f73d3038ddaffbab8f5748e69bba602588dcf71","tid":1631450,"uid":331388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:46:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14cf7f19b1d40960c5a155ee4877531b9797127c","tid":1631450,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:53:04.000Z","msg":"仲有記者係有專業知識去判斷應唔應該用傳媒話比國際知恐怖襲擊主義已經係香港苗頭"}]}